  "title": "Chonk Blocker Retro 1.1.0",
  "summary": "An elegant way out: closing the game now opens a cabinet-styled confirmation instead of quitting instantly, with a quit action reachable from settings and keyboard shortcuts.",
  "notes": [
    "Open a Leave the Arcade confirmation sheet when the window is closed, Alt+F4 or Ctrl+Q is pressed (\u2318Q on macOS), or the new QUIT GAME button in settings is used \u2014 the game no longer ends without asking.",
    "Keep playing is the safe default: Enter chooses the highlighted action, arrow keys switch between Keep Playing and Exit Game, and Escape always returns to the game.",
    "Pause emulation and mute audio while the sheet is open, and return keyboard focus to the game seamlessly on resume.",
    "Add a quit path reachable in fullscreen, where the window's close button is not available.",
    "Ship the 1.0.8 cartridge unchanged."
